## Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Python 3.11 | Core language |
| FastAPI | REST API framework |
| e5-large (sentence-transformers) | Embedding model for SEAT |
| Gemini API (Google AI Studio) | Bias explanation generation |
| Firebase Firestore | Real-time results sync with frontend |
| Docker | Containerisation for deployment |
| Hugging Face Spaces | Cloud deployment |

